      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This one-owner masterpiece has been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed monthly, preserving its original luster. The exterior features a flawless factory paint finish with a high-end ceramic coating, free of any rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, reflecting its accident-free history. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather seats still retain their original texture and scent, with zero signs of wear or bolster compression. All electronic systems, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium surround-sound system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a complete service history exclusively performed by the authorized dealership. It recently passed a comprehensive 150-point inspection with flying colors and sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
